rtes beaucoup à leur insoumission et à leur mécréance. Nous avons semé parmi eux l’animosité et la haine jusqu’au Jour de la Résurrection. Chaque fois qu’ils allument un feu de guerre, Allah l’éteint. Et ils s’emploient à répandre la corruption sur terre mais Allah n’aime pas les corrupteurs.\",\"tajweed\":[{\"class\":\"qalqalah\",\"start\":114,\"end\":115},{\"class\":\"ikhfa\",\"start\":130,\"end\":134},{\"class\":\"madd-wajib\",\"start\":148,\"end\":150},{\"class\":\"ghunnah\",\"start\":166,\"end\":168},{\"class\":\"idgham-bighunnah\",\"start\":176,\"end\":178},{\"class\":\"idgham-bighunnah\",\"start\":179,\"end\":181},{\"class\":\"idgham-mimi\",\"start\":187,\"end\":192},{\"class\":\"madd-jaiz\",\"start\":193,\"end\":196},{\"class\":\"ikhfa\",\"start\":198,\"end\":202},{\"class\":\"idgham-bilaghunnah\",\"start\":216,\"end\":221},{\"class\":\"idgham-bighunnah\",\"start\":235,\"end\":237},{\"class\":\"idgham-bighunnah\",\"start\":238,\"end\":240},{\"class\":\"idgham-bighunnah\",\"start\":246,\"end\":248},{\"class\":\"idgham-bighunnah\",\"start\":250,\"end\":252},{\"class\":\"madd-wajib\",\"start\":300,\"end\":302},{\"class\":\"madd-jaiz\",\"start\":339,\"end\":342},{\"class\":\"idgham-bilaghunnah\",\"start\":357,\"end\":359},{\"class\":\"idgham-bilaghunnah\",\"start\":360,\"end\":362},{\"class\":\"qalqalah\",\"start\":375,\"end\":376},{\"class\":\"idgham-bighunnah\",\"start\":426,\"end\":428},{\"class\":\"idgham-bighunnah\",\"start\":430,\"end\":432},{\"class\":\"madd-arid-lissukun\",\"start\":464,\"end\":466}]},\"surah\":\"$20\",\"index\":63}],[\"$\",\"$L1f\",\"64\",{\"verse\":{\"id\":734,\"number\":65,\"text\":\"وَلَوْ اَنَّ اَهْلَ الْكِتٰبِ اٰمَنُوْا وَاتَّقَوْا لَكَفَّرْنَا عَنْهُمْ سَيِّاٰتِهِمْ وَلَاَدْخَلْنٰهُمْ جَنّٰتِ النَّعِيْمِ\",\"translation_id\":\"Seandainya Ahlulkitab itu beriman dan bertakwa, niscaya Kami hapus kesalahan-kesalahan mereka dan tentu Kami masukkan mereka ke dalam surga-surga yang penuh kenikmatan. \",\"juz_id\":6,\"surah_id\":5,\"trans