t ce qui ne leur plaisait point, ils traitaient certains de menteurs et tuaient les autres.\",\"tajweed\":[{\"class\":\"qalqalah\",\"start\":4,\"end\":5},{\"class\":\"madd-jaiz\",\"start\":31,\"end\":35},{\"class\":\"madd-wajib\",\"start\":41,\"end\":43},{\"class\":\"madd-jaiz\",\"start\":62,\"end\":65},{\"class\":\"ikhfa\",\"start\":80,\"end\":82},{\"class\":\"ikhfa\",\"start\":85,\"end\":87},{\"class\":\"madd-wajib\",\"start\":97,\"end\":99},{\"class\":\"iqlab\",\"start\":112,\"end\":114},{\"class\":\"iqlab\",\"start\":115,\"end\":117},{\"class\":\"madd-jaiz\",\"start\":130,\"end\":135},{\"class\":\"ikhfa\",\"start\":137,\"end\":141},{\"class\":\"ikhfa\",\"start\":155,\"end\":157},{\"class\":\"ikhfa\",\"start\":158,\"end\":160},{\"class\":\"idgham-bighunnah\",\"start\":178,\"end\":180},{\"class\":\"idgham-bighunnah\",\"start\":181,\"end\":183},{\"class\":\"qalqalah\",\"start\":185,\"end\":186},{\"class\":\"madd-arid-lissukun\",\"start\":191,\"end\":193}]},\"surah\":\"$20\",\"index\":69}],[\"$\",\"$L1f\",\"70\",{\"verse\":{\"id\":740,\"number\":71,\"text\":\"وَحَسِبُوْٓا اَلَّا تَكُوْنَ فِتْنَةٌ فَعَمُوْا وَصَمُّوْا ثُمَّ تَابَ اللّٰهُ عَلَيْهِمْ ثُمَّ عَمُوْا وَصَمُّوْا كَثِيْرٌ مِّنْهُمْۗ وَاللّٰهُ بَصِيْرٌۢ بِمَا يَعْمَلُوْنَ\",\"translation_id\":\"Mereka mengira bahwa tidak akan terjadi fitnah (azab akibat dosa-dosa mereka). Oleh karena itu, mereka menjadi buta dan tuli. Setelah itu Allah menerima tobat mereka, kemudian banyak di antara mereka buta dan tuli (lagi). Allah Maha Melihat apa yang mereka kerjakan.\",\"juz_id\":6,\"surah_id\":5,\"transliteration\":\"wa ḫasibû allâ takûna fitnatun fa ‘amû wa shammû tsumma tâballâhu ‘alaihim tsumma ‘amû wa shammû katsîrum min-hum, wallâhu bashîrum bimâ ya‘malûn\",\"translation_en\":\"And they thought there would be no [resulting] punishment, so they became blind and deaf. Then Allāh turned to them in forgiveness; then [again] many of them became blind and deaf. And Allāh is Seeing of what they do.\",\"translation_de\":