 ainsi que les deux témoins seront conduits à donner le témoignage dans son aspect (le plus fiable) et craindront que d’autres serments ne viennent encore désavouer les leurs. Craignez Allah et écoutez. Allah ne guide point les gens pervers.\",\"tajweed\":[{\"class\":\"qalqalah\",\"start\":9,\"end\":10},{\"class\":\"madd-jaiz\",\"start\":11,\"end\":16},{\"class\":\"idgham-bighunnah\",\"start\":18,\"end\":23},{\"class\":\"qalqalah\",\"start\":55,\"end\":56},{\"class\":\"madd-jaiz\",\"start\":61,\"end\":64},{\"class\":\"madd-jaiz\",\"start\":76,\"end\":79},{\"class\":\"ikhfa\",\"start\":83,\"end\":88},{\"class\":\"iqlab\",\"start\":101,\"end\":103},{\"class\":\"iqlab\",\"start\":104,\"end\":106},{\"class\":\"madd-arid-lissukun\",\"start\":201,\"end\":203}]},\"surah\":\"$20\",\"index\":107}],[\"$\",\"$L1f\",\"108\",{\"verse\":{\"id\":778,\"number\":109,\"text\":\"۞ يَوْمَ يَجْمَعُ اللّٰهُ الرُّسُلَ فَيَقُوْلُ مَاذَٓا اُجِبْتُمْۗ قَالُوْا لَا عِلْمَ لَنَاۗ اِنَّكَ اَنْتَ عَلَّامُ الْغُيُوْبِ\",\"translation_id\":\"(Ingatlah) pada hari ketika Allah mengumpulkan para rasul, lalu Dia bertanya (kepada mereka), “Apa jawaban (kaummu) terhadap (seruan)-mu?” Mereka (para rasul) menjawab, “Kami tidak tahu (tentang itu). Sesungguhnya Engkaulah Yang Maha Mengetahui segala yang gaib.”\",\"juz_id\":7,\"surah_id\":5,\"transliteration\":\"yauma yajma‘ullâhur-rusula fa yaqûlu mâdzâ ujibtum, qâlû lâ ‘ilma lanâ, innaka anta ‘allâmul-ghuyûb\",\"translation_en\":\"[Be warned of] the Day when Allāh will assemble the messengers and say, \\\"What was the response you received?\\\" They will say, \\\"We have no knowledge. Indeed, it is You who is Knower of the unseen\\\" -\",\"translation_de\":\"An dem Tag, da Allah die Gesandten versammelt und dann sagt: Was wurde euch geantwortet?’, werden sie sagen: Wir haben kein Wissen (darüber). Du bist ja der Allwisser der verborgenen Dinge.\",\"translation_tr\":\"Allah'ın peygamberleri toplayıp da «Size ne cevap verildi» dediği gün, «Bizim hiçbir bilgi